{"tid":46232,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung A9 密碼轉左做PIN 碼點搞","createTime":"2016-12-19T13:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T14:00:06.000Z","uid":14793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"406a77ed793fa31fc335f25dbccf9c3d1efeb4b9","tid":46232,"uid":14793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:42:00.000Z","msg":"我老豆幾個月前買左部A9，部機係我幫佢SET<br />\n<br />\n果陣鎖機密碼Set 左3個英文3個數字<br />\n<br />\n跟住呢排我用佢部機睇，解鎖變左用Pin碼，即係要全數字<br />\n<br />\n我問我老豆搞過咩黎，佢話唔知，一直都用指紋解鎖<br />\n<br />\n問題就黎喇，如果Samsung restart 部機好似iPhone 咁要用passcode 首次解鎖咁佢咪解唔到部機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無辦法可以將pin 碼解鎖轉番做密碼，如果唔得唯有同佢拎去Samsung 到搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62f91ed37a23ef1dababc056c9768db195ae6e7","tid":46232,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整指紋果陣咪會入左 pin  碼 點會唔記得<br />\n俾返人啦"},{"pid":"7aa12e043f94dbdab449c9d4a71e75f5d917695d","tid":46232,"uid":14793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T14:00:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整指紋果陣咪會入左 pin  碼 點會唔記得<br />\n俾返人啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係本身用keyboard 入password, 可以入到英文同數字<br />\n<br />\n而家轉左 pin 碼， 整係入到數字<br />\n<br />\n我只係想問有無得將pin 碼果舊野轉番做keyboard 等我可以入番英文"}]}